<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nOH7WYFz27LeGPEs88iuSIOwLZo=/0x0:2168x2890/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VqA9AGxwKHMWJGtD8xPj92NrSo8=/0x0:2168x2890/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GkXpLnTGPcuuBdyJtNclXc7q_tc=/0x0:2168x2890/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/B0U4IQNykueEg4tPtZfkOlVx9Zw=/0x0:2168x2890/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FMTO9h1niyb8BFQh5OipEYNF1RM=/0x0:2168x2890/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wlLLD571mXQBnTsjmmS_xksbJVM=/0x0:2168x2890/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8ikSaD5-K0XQDORDCOLc0LG4_fg=/0x0:2168x2890/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Xmqd6P7cpOCQTUEcZzTYkgdsXPE=/0x0:2168x2890/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UhZnVMqbWPGBWBPG2FRd1fpdang=/0x0:2168x2890/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" data-upload-width="2168" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QicBMlKbdj7nHwXExNsdlaHNUH8=/0x0:2168x2890/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:2168x2890):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303948/IMG_0212.jpg">

</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
    <span class="e-image__meta">
      
        <figcaption><em>iPhone 11 Pro, 8X zoom, cropped to show detail</em></figcaption>
      
      
    </span>
  
</figure>

</div>
</div></div>
<p id="Ev6872">In short, Google’s claim of significantly improved telephoto images is not hyperbole. They are remarkable. It’s notably better than what the iPhone 11 Pro can produce at max zoom.</p>
<p id="hmioMY">And that’s really why you’re here, isn’t it? To see if the Pixel 4 can take back the “best smartphone camera” crown from the iPhone 11 Pro. </p>
<div class="c-float-right c-float-hang"><aside id="GFDKeZ"><q>Apple’s Deep Fusion software update is right around the corner</q></aside></div>
<p id="JrU5Cc">Well, I can’t answer that yet. I’m sorry. When <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/17/20868727/apple-iphone-11-pro-max-review-camera-battery-life-screen-midnight-green-price">Nilay reviewed the iPhone 11 Pro last month</a>, he was forced to admit that the Pixel 4 was waiting in the wings. This month, as I review the Pixel 4, I’m forced to admit that a forthcoming software update for the iPhone 11 Pro will bring Apple’s “Deep Fusion” algorithms to its camera and improve performance in medium-light conditions. </p>
<p id="utXJiH">I have been testing Deep Fusion (aka “sweater mode”) in beta on the iPhone 11, but I’m not going to compare shipping software on one phone to beta software on another. That’s not fair to anybody.</p>
<p id="ajjAsH">Still, I do think it’s useful to look at some comparison photos and to talk through some of the features Google has added to its camera stack. Because what I’ve learned in reviewing the Pixel 4 is that Google has improved on the Pixel 3, but it’s not a massive year-over-year change. (On most of the photos below, you can click for a full-resolution image.)</p>
<div id="sMOKza">
<div class="c-imageslider" data-cid="apps/imageslider-1587250174_1606_229365" data-cdata='{"caption":"&lt;em&gt;Pixel 4 left; iPhone 11 Pro right&lt;/em&gt;","image_left":{"ratio":"*","original_url":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303961/B_Pixel_4_sample_photo_.jpg","network":"verge","bgcolor":"#ffffff","pinterest_enabled":false,"caption":null,"credit":null,"focal_area":{"top_left_x":0,"top_left_y":0,"bottom_right_x":4032,"bottom_right_y":3024},"bounds":[0,0,4032,3024],"uploaded_size":{"width":4032,"height":3024},"focal_point":null,"asset_id":19303961,"asset_credit":null,"alt_text":""},"image_right":{"ratio":"*","original_url":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19303962/iPhone_11_Pro_sample_photo_001.jpg","network":"verge","bgcolor":"#ffffff","pinterest_enabled":false,"caption":null,"credit":null,"focal_area":{"top_left_x":0,"top_left_y":0,"bottom_right_x":4032,"bottom_right_y":3024},"bounds":[0,0,4032,3024],"uploaded_size":{"width":4032,"height":3024},"focal_point":null,"asset_id":19303962,"asset_credit":null,"alt_text":""},"credit":null}'>
